			"editorData": {
				"HowToTrigger": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "- Load up GustavDev/SCL_Main_A\r\n- \"goto 678 18 41\"\r\n- Interact with S_COL_TadpolingCentre_DarkUrgePod_1c7028d3-bb96-4bc5-8fb6-8b6e1d6a5e27\r\n- This interaction will be disabled if you enter the Colony without the Dark Urge in party/camp (meaning the DU would not exist in this playthrough). This only happens if you enter the Colony through gameplay or the debugbook. It will get re-enabled if you recruit the Dark Urge via debug."
				},
